The cleric aggro is a mess, clerics getting beat on left and right in my Trak raid last night.<br>
<br>
Screwing with clerics was the biggest mistake Verant could have made.  Most clerics are already dissatisfied with their class, especially now that the only benefit they have to offer over other priests is Res (hello paladin), CH, and some very high level spells that only really shine vs uber mobs.<br>
